messages.text: How is Sadie, Mr. Danton?
Who’s this!?
My name’s Lyn Vandemeer.
I was … I am one of your daughter’s classmates at Munroe High.
Sadie’s still in the hospital, in a coma.
She might not live.
I didn’t get to her … quick enough.
I’m so sorry. :’(
Was GrimR involved?
What the hell do you know about GrimR!?
Do you know who this GrimR is, Lyn!?
No!!
But … GrimR counselled me to kill myself, too.
GrimR told me I’d fly to heaven.
When I jumped off the Ecclesiastical Tower downtown.
Jesus! That’s at least eight storeys high!
I didn’t make it to heaven, Mr. Danton.
I landed in hell.
I spent six months in the hospital...
recovering, with spine, knee and brain trauma.
I’m sorry, Lyn.
I’m doing better now, though! Things did get better – after.
I never should have attempted it.
Suicide is so ugly and violent – it hurts everybody around you.
I never would have attempted it if it wasn’t for GrimR.
It takes courage to live, weakness to die.
I want to help you find GrimR, Mr. Danton!
I don’t know if you should
GrimR has to be stopped!
Sadie told me you worked for a national security agency, as an operative.
Yeah.
That’s why I’ve been away from home so much. I wasn’t there for my daughter...
Don’t blame yourself!
I do blame myself.
But I blame GrimR more!
Maybe you can help me, Lyn, since you go to Munroe. You’re on the inside.
Yes!!
We have to stop this...killing spree. Life is too precious – I know.
But when we catch GrimR..
I’m going to terminate that bastard!
two hours later
I just talked to one of the vice-principals at Munroe – Mr. Slezak.
He wasn’t very helpful.
He didn’t seem too concerned about Scarlett and Sadie.
He thinks the recent student suicides and attempts are just a ‘fad’! :-(
Well he just went on my suspects list.
I’m in my car patrolling the school catchment area..
Monitoring phone and computer communications for any suicide talk -
or reference to GrimR.
How do you do that!?
Don’t ask. It’s strictly off the record. ;-)
Can’t you hack into GrimR’s phone or computer and find out where
He, or she, probably uses new phones all the time, throws the old ones away.
I’m going to talk to the principal when she gets back.
I’ve got something!
A text conversation!
Here, look:
But a double suicide is soooo romantic, Scott!! :’)
I don’t know about
Two lovers dying in each other’s arms.. :’)
Together for all of eternity!
Everybody remembers it, Scott! Everybody talks about it!
Avy and Scott are seniors at Munroe High, Mr. Danton!!
I’m zeroing in on the location of Avy’s phone!
She lives at 54 Apple Lane! Not far from the school!
I’m biking there right now!
I’m one block over! Closing fast!
Poison is a super quick and effective method, Scott!
Yeah? What about stabbing!?
Just think, no more parental or peer pressure!
Just sweet, everlasting peace! :’)
Lovers forever and ever..
Oh my God!!
The front door of Avy’s house is broken right off its hinges, Mr. Danton!!
There’s screaming coming from inside!!
What should I
I’m inside the house, Lyn.
I broke down the door.
What happened to Avy and
I’m fine, Lyn.
Scott and I were just discussing ‘Romeo & Juliet’.
You know, the Shakespeare play we’re studying in Mr. Slezak’s English class!
Where Romeo and Juliet kill themselves at the end. :-|
Oh, right. I’m
I’ve already apologized, Lyn. And paid for the door. :-/
How are you feeling these days, Lyn?
It’s … you!!
Yes, it’s me. Your former best friend, remember?
WORST friend, you mean!!
I hear you’re trying to stir up trouble at school now.
How did you
Ending one’s own life is a choice, Lyn, as we discussed at length. A right.
You have no right to interfere in a person’s
YOU INTERFERED!!
You urged me to kill myself!!
I was just thinking about it; all depressed..
But you told me just what to do!
What pills to take and where to get them –
so I’d be in the right mood to jump off
Don’t be bitter just because you botched your release, bitch! >:-(
You can always try again.
I’ll even help you again. :-)
I don’t need your ‘help’, asshole! I’m doing ok!
You’re the bitter, sick, twisted one!
Pervertedly preying on vulnerable girls!
SHUT THE HELL UP, YOU STUPID BLONDE BITCH
YOU’RE GOING TO SHUT THE HELL UP, ASSWIPE!
I’M GOING TO SEE TO THAT – PERSONALLY!
Who’s this!?
Who are you – ‘Cole’!?
I’m Sadie’s father, shithead!
And I’m going to track you down and
Poor Sadie almost died on your ‘watch’ … Dad! >;-)
You’re not much of a father, from what she told me.
Never there when a teenaged daughter needs her daddy the most.
Leaving sad little Sadie to fend all for herself. :-((
You’re going to find out just what kind of father I am!
Father to ALL of the troubled young women you prey upon!
I’m going to hunt you down and
Here’s a clue, Dad: what was Lyn doing to ‘help’ Sadie? :-??
In her hour of need.
What the hell are you -
You can’t monitor the life of every Munroe High loser girl online!
So many sad, suffering, self-pitying, little bitches..
And so little time – that they have left..
To join GrimR’s SUICIDE SOCIETY! >:-))
